ing: 1 (.7 ounce) package dry Italian-style salad dressing mix
des: "This is a yummy beef dip that we make for every party. Serve it with pieces of pumpernickel bread, or in a bread bowl made from a round pumpernickel loaf.  Very easy and tasty!"
ins: In a medium bowl, mix sour cream, mayonnaise, dry Italian-style salad dressing mix and dried beef. Cover and chill in the refrigerator 8 hours, or overnight, before serving.
